## Titanic

```{r libraries, echo = TRUE, include=FALSE}
library(conflicted)
library(here)
library(janitor)
library(tidyverse)
library(tidymodels)
library(workflows)
library(vroom)
library(skimr)
```

```{r titanic, echo = TRUE, message = FALSE}
titanic <- vroom("../input/train.csv", .name_repair = make_clean_names) %>%
  mutate(survived = as_factor(survived))

titanic
```



